00:24:01,321 --> 00:24:02,363
Apa?

487
00:24:02,446 --> 00:24:04,488
Kau harus memberitahunya, Ben.

488
00:24:05,322 --> 00:24:07,655
Aku tak peduli
jika kau tak bisa membuktikannya.

489
00:24:08,155 --> 00:24:09,197
