00:29:29,479 --> 00:29:30,896
Hai.

576
00:29:34,605 --> 00:29:35,980
Aku...

577
00:29:38,064 --> 00:29:40,064
Kau ingat Jack.

578
00:29:40,147 --> 00:29:41,814
Ya, kami pernah bertemu.

579
00:29:43,856 --> 00:29:46,690
Dengar, aku tak perlu tinggal lama...

