00:30:04,525 --> 00:30:05,608
Aku harus kehilangan segalanya...

586
00:30:05,691 --> 00:30:07,067
Sebelum bisa membantu diriku sendiri.

587
00:30:23,693 --> 00:30:25,193
Addison.

588
00:30:25,735 --> 00:30:27,277
Kita berhasil.

589
00:30:27,527 --> 00:30:30,444
Trevor sudah pergi
dan kita berhasil melewati malam.

